      "text": "The established view sees ICT as a hard technology (Dron, 2013). What can be done with hard technology is fixed in advance either by embedding it in the technology or \"in inflexible human processes, rules and procedures needed for the technology’s operation\" (Dron, 2013, p. 35). "
